Question: What do you like/dislike about public transportation.
Answer:
To some extent I like public transportation but to some I don't like it.

I like public transportation because it is environmentally friendly. People share buses and metro so they don't have to drive their own car which causes pollution to the atmosphere. in addition, public transportation is more convenient for travelers who don't know the city well. It is also much safer.

I don't like it because the time is not flexible and  some times it is too crowded.